yahoogroups.com] On Behalf Of hijbul_bd
&gt; Sent: Friday, June 06, 2008 8:27 AM
&gt; To: archive-crawler@ &lt;mailto:archive-crawler%40yahoogroups.com&gt;
yahoogroups.com
&gt; Subject: [archive-crawler] Crawling 100 million pages
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; Dear All
&gt; 
&gt; I would like to crawl 100 million pages with in a month for crawling 
&gt; research. As far i know some research crawler(IRLbot(6 billion pages in 
&gt; 41 days), polybot(120 millions pages in 19 days)) can download huge 
&gt; pages in short amount of time wich is not open source. In 2005 
&gt; according to some blog site Heritrix can download about 20 miilion 
&gt; pages in a month. What is the speed of current Heritrix version and How 
&gt; can I speed up heritrix to download 100 million or at least 50 million 
&gt; pages with in a month. Are there any ohter open source crawler which 
&gt; can do this?
&gt; 
&gt; Thanks in Advance
&gt; Hijbul Alam
&gt;




